OL,3,CSkeletal remains found at multi-storey
OL,4,Ccar park are human
OL,6,FSkeletal remains found at an old multi-
OL,7,Fstorey car park in Newcastle-under-
OL,8,FLyme have been confirmed to be human
OL,9,Fby the police.
OL,11,FOfficers are now standing guard at
OL,12,FMidway car park where work is underway
OL,13,Fto transform the building into 111
OL,14,Fapartments.
