OL,3,CSkeletal remains found at multi-storey
OL,4,Ccar park are human
OL,6,FA Staffordshire Police spokeswoman
OL,7,Fsaid, "We were called to reports of
OL,8,Fskeletal remains being found on a
OL,9,Fconstruction site on The Midway,
OL,10,Fformerly the Midway car park,
OL,11,FNewcastle-under-Lyme. A scene has been
OL,12,Fput in place while we carry out
OL,13,Finitial enquiries."
OL,15,FWork has paused while the developers
OL,16,Fare helping police with their
OL,17,Finquiries.
